snippet.title: Princess Quest Mahjong Sword PCM showcase
snippet.description: Composed by KID, this game was one of the few games that used only the PC9801-86 PCM output to make music. Similar to PPZ8, its driver allow you to use multiple sample channels at the same time. The game has a YM2203 soundtrack as well for compatibility, but it's entirely different.
